					<outline text="Today's talk came about from a random meeting with &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brendan_Eich&quot;&gt;Brendan Eich&lt;/a&gt; at a party early this year. I had heard him once on a Gillmor Gang &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.itconversations.com/shows/detail156.html&quot;&gt;podcast&lt;/a&gt;, and found our philosophies more or less match." created="Thu, 16 Aug 2007 17:50:57 GMT"/>
