			<outline text="August 1" created="Wed, 01 Aug 2007 05:00:01 GMT">
				<outline text="Helping Doc transition" created="Wed, 01 Aug 2007 23:59:46 GMT">
					<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://images.scripting.com/archiveScriptingCom/2007/07/29/docbyscott.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://images.scripting.com/archiveScriptingCom/2007/08/01/doc.jpg&quot; width=&quot;105&quot; height=&quot;138&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; align=&quot;right&quot; hspace=&quot;15&quot; vspace=&quot;5&quot; alt=&quot;A picture named doc.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Doc Searls is &lt;a href=&quot;http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/docsearls/&quot;&gt;moving his blog&lt;/a&gt; to a Harvard-hosted WordPress site." created="Wed, 01 Aug 2007 23:59:52 GMT"/>
					<outline text="I'm helping him do this transition, the first part is done. His editorial tool, an outliner, is working with WordPress, and knock wood, praise Murphy, he'll be updating that blog, and we'll be archiving the original blog. " created="Thu, 02 Aug 2007 00:03:59 GMT"/>
					<outline text="If you're reading his blog look for new posts on the WordPress site, and you can subscribe to his newly located &lt;a href=&quot;http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/docsearls/feed/&quot;&gt;RSS feed&lt;/a&gt;. We'll be redirecting that as well." created="Thu, 02 Aug 2007 00:04:52 GMT"/>
